title: Benebone Indestructible Dog Chew Toy Gift Box for Aggressive Chewers with Wishbone, Fishbone, Stick & Zaggler, Long Lasting Boredom Breakers, 100% Real Flavours, For Small Dogs, Made in the USA.
features: FOUR-PACK OF CHEWING FUN – A cracking bundle of dog bones and dog toys indestructible, made for little but mighty chewers. Includes 1x Bacon Wishbone, 1x Maple Stick, 1x Bacon Zaggler, and 1x Jack Salmon Fishbone. Perfect for keeping your pup busy. Best suited for small dogs up to 2 stone (14 kg), like Jack Russells and Dachshunds.

LONG-LASTING DOG CHEWS – Got a small but determined chewer? Our dog toys are tough as old boots and built to handle relentless gnawing. Designed with a clever curved shape for easy gripping, so your pup can crack on with a proper chew.

100% REAL FLAVOURS – No dodgy rubbish here. We use real flavours like bacon, fish, and wood—none of that artificial nonsense. Just two ingredients: proper flavour and durable nylon. No nasties, no chemicals—just top-quality dog chews your pup will love.

KNOW WHEN TO BIN IT – Our dog bones are built to last, but even they won’t go on forever. Swap it out after a month, or sooner if your pup’s had a real go. If more than a sugar cube’s worth is missing, time for a fresh one.

ABOUT BENEBONE – Designed in the USA, we’re all about long-lasting dog toys packed with real flavour to keep your pup happy. Got a question? Give us a bell – you’ll be chatting with a real human whose job is to keep you and your pup smiling.
description: Product Description How long does a Benebone last? In a few weeks, maybe a month, it’s usually time to retire. It varies from one dog to the next, so keep a close eye out for wear and tear. If you’re handy, try smoothing gnarly spots with a wood file or heavy grit sandpaper to prolong life. Are Benebones edible? Benebones have just the right amount of tantalising flavour to enhance your pup’s chewing experience. Our bones are made for a good chew session, but are not edible treats to be consumed. Watch for signs of wear and replace when necessary! Which size is best for my pup? We’ve got you covered with tiny bones for cute little 15-pounders, Giant bones for hundred-pounders and everything in between. If your pup is between sizes or an enthusiastic chewer, consider sizing up. Your pup will thank you! What are the ingredients? Benebones are made with USA-sourced nylon and flavoured with a variety of real ingredients like yummy bacon, chicken, peanut, beef tripe, maple wood and jack salmon. What’s different about a puppy Benebone? Our puppy Benebones are a tad softer for puppies without all their adult teeth just yet. Once your dog has adult teeth, it’s time to move on to our regular chews
